npm init will create pacakage.json-file
or npm ini--yes

To set the default value-
1. npm config set init-author-name "shweta"
2. npm set init-license "MIT"

To set the default value:
1. npm, config get -author-name "
2. npm  confid get init -license

To delete the default values
1. npm config delete init-license -author.name

